title: [Yegharren Plain, Veldt]
description: A few graceful trees stand tall above the grassy veldt, their flowering branches attracting swarms of buzzing bees and a few jewel-like hummingbirds.  The shrieking cry of some distant bird of prey echoes faintly on the wind.

A few graceful trees stand tall above the grassy veldt, their flowering branches attracting a few buzzing bees and other insects even in the darkness of the night.  The shrieking cry of some distant bird of prey echoes faintly on the wind.
